    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of October 25 article on decline in television ratings for sports events</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article on Wednesday about a decline in television ratings for sports events misstated the figure and the change for this year's National Basketball Association finals on NBC. The rating was 11.6, not 11.7; it was a 2.7 percent increase from last year's, not an 18 percent drop.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>An article on Wednesday about a decline in television ratings for sports events misstated the figure and the change for this year's National Basketball Association finals on NBC. The rating was 11.6, not 11.7; it was a 2.7 percent increase from last year's, not an 18 percent drop.</p>
      </block>
